{"thag3.1:0.1":"Theragatha 3.1 ","thag3.1:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.1:0.4":"Anganikabharadvajattheragatha ","thag3.1:1.1":"“Ayoni suddhimanvesam, ","thag3.1:1.2":"aggim paricarim vane; ","thag3.1:1.3":"Suddhimaggam ajananto, ","thag3.1:1.4":"akasim amaram tapam. ","thag3.1:2.1":"Tam sukhena sukham laddham, ","thag3.1:2.2":"passa dhammasudhammatam; ","thag3.1:2.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag3.1:2.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thag3.1:3.1":"Brahmabandhu pure asim, ","thag3.1:3.2":"idani khomhi brahmano; ","thag3.1:3.3":"Tevijjo nhatako camhi, ","thag3.1:3.4":"sottiyo camhi vedagu”ti. ","thag3.1:3.5":"… Anganikabharadvajo thero …. "}